ðŸ§© 1. What $process Actually Is
In YARA-L, the dollar-sign variables (like $event, $process, $login, $dns) are just labels that you give to specific event filters inside your ruleâ€™s events: section.
They arenâ€™t special keywords â€” you can name them whatever helps describe what that event is doing.

So when you see:

